reviews.review_text: Nice sounding FM recording Great show, great sounding FM. I have Dozin' at the Knick and I know there's a Miller board of this show. But still, I really dig this FM. They were on fire during the Spring of 1990. A lot of highlights. Saw them at the Knickerbocker Arena a few years later. Great place.
